[{"id":1,"title":"The Brave Chick","code":"CHICK2026","story":"Once upon a time, there was a little chick named Kiki. Kiki was small but very brave. One day the wind blew strong and blew Kiki away from mama. Kiki cried but then remembered mama said brave hearts never give up. So Kiki flapped her tiny wings and walked through the tall grass until she found her way home. Mama hugged Kiki and said 'I am so proud of you my brave chick!' From that day, everyone in the farmyard knew Kiki as the bravest chick of all. The end."}]